ly a poor predictor of both its proximate and ultimate fates. This is\nbecause there is in general little correlation between the origin of CGM gas\nand its fate owing to substantial mixing while in the CGM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Oct 2019 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-15"}
