g to the experimental outcomes, the hybrid cooperative\nframework exhibits better performance in terms of both runtime and quality of\nobtained solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 2019 02:16:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-07"}
