new magnetic phases and extend the\nBose-Hubbard model when the atoms are placed in an optical lattice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 2019 08:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 9 May 2020 05:59:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-12"}
