synthesize prior research on parallel optimization in OR, focusing on\ncomputational studies published in the period 2008-2017. Finally, we suggest\nresearch directions for parallel optimization in OR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 2019 13:50:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
